{"tid":1624762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔係廣告】元氣x榴槤壽司！！Starbucks咖啡x瑞典魔性臭魚！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:55:10.000Z","uid":86942,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45a9c73c71a8813560f94189de15294246982909","tid":1624762,"uid":86942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"放題食過一次榴槤炸彈，香味驚為天人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果陣香味<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">芳香四溢</span></span>、一傳千里，由內到外再到番內咁連珠爆發，啲<span style=\"color: gold;\">香味吸曬入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地毯</span></span>一留就留幾個星期，入埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">冷氣槽</span></span>就真係洗幾多次都唔掂！唔知既人路過真係以為去左<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榴槤樂園</span></span>！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvWjVfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvWjVfU.jpg&h=08a5664f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是，一向好鍾意食壽司既我，諗到神仙都羡慕既美味佳餚──<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榴槤壽司</span></span>，好可惜明將壽司已經創新不再，而且大家似乎都對<span style=\"color: orange;\">元氣情有獨鍾</span>。所以我諗過，雖然我地唔可以帶榴槤呢啲外來食物入去，但如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">自備榴槤醬料/漿/碎</span>[/size=5]入去添加風味又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5OVtzs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5OVtzs.png&h=9e1c28f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通既壽司上面<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">輕輕一抹</span></span>就可以變成榴槤壽司，再加上元氣呢個<span style=\"color: orange;\">火車直送gimmick</span>，只需要將榴槤漿放係<span style=\"color: violet;\">車軌上空</span>，火車就會<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高速滑過</span></span>並沾上醬料<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">昇格為榴槤壽司</span></span>！！聽落係咪非常吸引呢？唔知大家對呢個食法有冇興趣？記得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千奇唔好落錯係人地既壽司上面呀</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n雖然最近元氣好受歡迎，但即使冇位坐都可以係店<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">門口排隊</span></span>既時候食榴槤<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過下口癮</span></span>先！如果真係等唔切既，都可以買外賣<span style=\"color: orange;\">即場加上榴槤風味</span>，順便<span style=\"color: violet;\">派比周圍挨餓排隊既客人</span>推廣下創新食法，試過聞過既客人可能會<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂愛上</span></span>榴槤壽司<span style=\"color: red;\">搞到連元氣都冇興趣食添</span>！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>簡單</strong></span></span>得黎又咁有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">創意</span></strong></span>既食法，大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔會唔去幫手推廣下掛</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBHxHQnuJsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUBHxHQnuJsA&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=37983fa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBHxHQnuJsA</a><br />\n而至於另一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">創新食法</span></span>，係一個好鍾意飲咖啡又好鍾意<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瑞典鹽醃鯡魚罐頭</span></span>既人諗出黎既，睇過條片就知道呢個聞名全球既罐頭係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">重口味過榴槤幾多倍</span></span>。聽人講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一邊飲咖啡一邊嘆鹽醃鯡魚</span></span>味道簡直天作之合！可惜我唔知邊度有得買，如果搵到既我都想搵日<span style=\"color: red;\">一邊嘆Starbucks既極品咖啡配上呢個鹽醃鯡魚做小食</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過要注意番，個罐頭<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好圓好易跌</span></span>，千奇<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千奇唔好倒瀉</span></span>左係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地毯</span></span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梳化</span></span>等等<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">難以清潔既地方</span></span>，唔係就會好頭痕架啦！！<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n除左呢兩個<del>美心</del>、呀唔係、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">美食組合</span></span>之外，大J都推介左唔少<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">等待大家發掘</span></span>既美食組合，如果大家諗到既一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">po上黎分享</span></span>下呀！<br />\n美食channel : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/JStud1o/search?query=%E8%87%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FJStud1o%2Fsearch%3Fquery%3D%25E8%2587%25AD&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=20ca5d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/JStud1o/search?query=%E8%87%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">廣傳分享</span></span>，比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔同年齡</span></span>、[size=5]<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔同承擔能力</span></span>既人都可以開開心心加入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>美食家</ins></strong></span></span>行列，除左日日撳飛之外都可以<span style=\"color: violet;\">大飽口福</span>～～"},{"pid":"4b411b5b410d015254d4454cdf1c747d66f49262","tid":1624762,"uid":177330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69606f5ad1fae7d7d2a42b5f6aebf76f3f34ed3f","tid":1624762,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有車人士召集區<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.5 黨鐵和你塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"881b2dc13d8b419cdaa66f08539f38d015f04fae","tid":1624762,"uid":159890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"CLS 文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008cb6b164ea094e4942d684fa5d6d95ba7bb130","tid":1624762,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"Pacific 喺華潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}